That is a good change-up, dangled the carrot and he fell in the trap

This will brighten up Bangladesh; they were desperately in search of a wicket

dismissalComment.html: Has he nicked it? Bangladesh seem adamant they've got him nicking to the keeper, Nazmul reviews. They're all very excited and convinced. That was a scorcher on back of a length and got steepling bounce, jagged back and Shan tried to prod it down to mid-off, Bangladesh have got it absolutely right; there is a deflection on the ultra-edge and it's a successful review. Pakistan captain departs! That decision to bowl first is proving correct so far, Shan is arguing with the umpire and says the ball clipped the pads and the technology got it wrong, Richard tells him to keep walking back to the hut, Shan is furious and not happy with the decision. Third umpire might have made that decision in haste, ball was close to the pad but we gotta move on
